        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>Healthcare Safety Solutions</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              Advanced systems designed to enhance patient safety and improve healthcare outcomes.
