        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl text-center mb-8">About Us</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto max-w-[900px] text-gray-700 md:text-xl text-center mb-12">
          PIDANA Technologies is committed to innovating for a safer world. Our mission is to develop cutting-edge
          technologies that enhance safety and improve healthcare outcomes. We are driven by our core values of
          Integrity, Innovation, and Quality.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Leadership</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
          {founders.map((founder, index) => (
            <Card key={index}>
              <CardHeader>
                <CardTitle>{founder.name}</CardTitle>
              </CardHeader>
              <CardContent>
                {founder.bio}
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          ))}
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Key Milestones</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Foundation of PIDANA Technologies</li>
          <li>Development of our first healthcare safety solution</li>
          <li>Launch of fall prevention technology</li>
          <li>Announcement of EyEagle project</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="solutions" class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gray-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl text-center mb-8">Our Solutions</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <ShieldCheck className="w-8 h-8 mb-2" />
              <CardTitle>Healthcare Solutions</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              Our healthcare solutions focus on fall prevention systems, monitoring technologies, and safety
