            <CardContent>
              We offer consulting services and develop customized technology solutions for the healthcare and safety
              industries. Our team works closely with clients to address unique challenges and requirements.
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section id="technologies" class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl text-center mb-8">Our Technologies</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>AI and Machine Learning</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              Advanced algorithms that power predictive analytics and intelligent decision-making in our solutions.
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>LIDAR Technology</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              High-precision sensing capabilities for accurate spatial awareness and object detection.
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>IoT Integration</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              Seamless connectivity and data exchange between devices for comprehensive monitoring and control.
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader>
              <CardTitle>Sensor Technologies</CardTitle>
            </CardHeader>
            <CardContent>
              Cutting-edge sensors for real-time data collection and environmental monitoring.
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg">
            These technologies form the foundation of our innovative solutions, including our upcoming product, EyEagle.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
